        "username": "jdksbskbsbs",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/f6c823/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-05-12T19:37:43.053Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi! I think that the name “Signal” should not get transliterated to the Arabic “سيجنال” because Arabic doesn’t have the /g/ sound, so it looks like “Sijnal”.<br>\nThis is also mentioned in <a href=\"https://wiki.localizationlab.org/index.php/Signal\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Signal - Localization Lab Wiki</a> under the Translation Guidelines section, but I don’t know if it’s official Signal guidelines and/or up to date.<br>\nLastly, if it’s decided to continue the transliteration, at least consider transliterating the App name as it’s currently English, which is inconsistent with what you’ll find in the app.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/a/9/a9c77ea59a698928af9d93e3a43251baf20de1ca.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/a9c77ea59a698928af9d93e3a43251baf20de1ca\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/a/9/a9c77ea59a698928af9d93e3a43251baf20de1ca.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"odW6GZXohiOxC77GI5tKKiPtEHU\" width=\"319\" height=\"312\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">319×312 19.3 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\nApp icon showing English name<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/c/d/cd078fc60b8c4619651776372ba67a99e4d76d54.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/cd078fc60b8c4619651776372ba67a99e4d76d54\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/c/d/cd078fc60b8c4619651776372ba67a99e4d76d54_2_689x102.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"tfM55HCFyn4zuwDweTzOHrZDywk\" width=\"689\" height=\"102\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/c/d/cd078fc60b8c4619651776372ba67a99e4d76d54_2_689x102.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/c/d/cd078fc60b8c4619651776372ba67a99e4d76d54_2_1033x153.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/c/d/cd078fc60b8c4619651776372ba67a99e4d76d54.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"2C2C2E\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1290×191 8.78 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\nInside the app, the Arabic transliteration is used.<br>\nThanks.</p>",
