        "created_at": "2025-05-29T18:27:19.895Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hello <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/jdksbskbsbs\">@jdksbskbsbs</a> ,</p>\n<p>Thanks for this feedback! We chose to transliterate Signal as “سيجنال” for quite a few reasons, the most prominent being that “Signal” has been transliterated in-app in Arabic since the onset of being localized years ago.</p>\n<p>As for the app name - thank you for pointing this out!</p>\n<p>Best regards,</p>\n<p>Phil</p>",
